00:01:27.635 --> 00:01:31.200
=The Maid=

00:01:31.540 --> 00:01:33.920
=Episode 8=

00:01:35.640 --> 00:01:37.760
Lady Ye scalded my cousin without cause

00:01:37.880 --> 00:01:39.400
and damaged imperial property.

00:01:39.760 --> 00:01:40.680
Beat her to death!

00:01:49.280 --> 00:01:50.240
Please judge wisely.

00:01:51.400 --> 00:01:52.640
It was Lady Jifu.

00:01:52.640 --> 00:01:53.480
She was drunk

00:01:53.480 --> 00:01:55.560
and dropped the imperial gift
into the brazier.

00:01:55.700 --> 00:01:57.000
She tried to grab it barehanded.

00:01:57.160 --> 00:01:58.800
I moved to stop her,

00:01:58.920 --> 00:02:00.080
and Lady Jifu kicked

00:02:00.080 --> 00:02:01.520
the brazier over.

00:02:01.520 --> 00:02:03.080
- You...
- Still dare to argue?

00:02:03.760 --> 00:02:04.960
Someone!

00:02:04.960 --> 00:02:06.320
Slap her fifty times!

00:02:09.880 --> 00:02:10.880
Your Highness?

00:02:17.600 --> 00:02:18.480
I invited you

00:02:18.480 --> 00:02:20.040
to enjoy moonlight and wine tonight.

00:02:20.440 --> 00:02:22.000
Had you come sooner,

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:23.640
this wouldn't have happened.

00:02:28.704 --> 00:02:30.144
(She prepared in advance.)

00:02:30.304 --> 00:02:31.616
(Today's plan is ruined.)

00:02:35.120 --> 00:02:36.120
Your Highness,

00:02:36.320 --> 00:02:38.120
I failed in managing the household,

00:02:38.120 --> 00:02:40.200
letting them go too far.

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:42.960
Shen Yuanjin,

00:02:42.960 --> 00:02:44.160
she scalded me.

00:02:44.160 --> 00:02:46.040
And you dismiss it lightly?

00:02:46.624 --> 00:02:47.744
The ladies' banquet tomorrow

00:02:47.744 --> 00:02:49.360
will gather noble ladies and matriarchs.

00:02:50.120 --> 00:02:51.920
I want no further incidents

00:02:52.240 --> 00:02:53.960
that shame the mansion

00:02:54.240 --> 00:02:56.480
or anger the Empress Dowager.

00:02:57.520 --> 00:02:58.720
Lady Ye

00:02:58.840 --> 00:03:00.200
shall stay in her chamber then.

00:03:06.760 --> 00:03:08.200
Arrange it as you see fit.

00:03:10.600 --> 00:03:11.560
Your Highness,

00:03:11.560 --> 00:03:13.720
I wish to attend too.

00:03:35.440 --> 00:03:36.520
Want to kill me with pain?

00:03:37.440 --> 00:03:38.464
Get out!

00:03:42.840 --> 00:03:44.760
That's premium burn ointment.

00:03:45.280 --> 00:03:46.560
It prevents scarring.

00:03:47.480 --> 00:03:49.840
You're the protagonist tomorrow.

00:03:50.360 --> 00:03:52.120
Don't let this distract you.

00:03:54.560 --> 00:03:55.720
Protagonist?

00:04:00.480 --> 00:04:02.320
I'm just a puppet

00:04:02.920 --> 00:04:05.120
dressed prettily

00:04:05.240 --> 00:04:06.800
to play your political theater.

00:04:07.200 --> 00:04:09.040
So the imperial merchants will know

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:10.800
how much the Empress Dowager values me.

00:04:15.240 --> 00:04:17.360
What nonsense are you spouting now?

00:04:20.320 --> 00:04:21.920
You sold me to Jiangnan

00:04:22.800 --> 00:04:24.560
for imperial merchants' money,

00:04:25.200 --> 00:04:26.720
funding the Emperor's reign.

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:28.880
The Empress Dowager,

00:04:28.960 --> 00:04:29.880
you,

00:04:30.240 --> 00:04:31.080
my aunt,

00:04:31.400 --> 00:04:32.720
all profit.

00:04:34.320 --> 00:04:36.680
But did any of you
care about my feelings?

00:04:36.960 --> 00:04:38.320
I don't want to marry!

00:04:38.320 --> 00:04:39.400
Lin Jifu!

00:04:41.080 --> 00:04:42.920
This marriage isn't yours to refuse.

00:04:42.920 --> 00:04:44.720
What gives you the right to command me?

00:04:46.560 --> 00:04:48.160
You and your mother

00:04:48.160 --> 00:04:50.320
are lapdogs leeching off my family.

00:04:52.600 --> 00:04:53.840
Keep causing trouble,

00:04:54.120 --> 00:04:56.080
and I'll have the Empress Dowager

00:04:56.400 --> 00:04:58.320
confine you till the wedding.

00:05:04.160 --> 00:05:05.040
Yuanjin.

00:05:05.040 --> 00:05:06.624
Yuanjin, I was wrong.

00:05:06.624 --> 00:05:07.600
I just don't want

00:05:07.600 --> 00:05:09.680
to marry alone in Jiangnan.

00:05:09.920 --> 00:05:10.976
There are merchants

00:05:11.080 --> 00:05:12.440
in the capital too.

00:05:12.736 --> 00:05:13.600
I'll never

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:15.280
take euphoria powder again.

00:05:15.400 --> 00:05:16.280
I beg you.

00:05:16.360 --> 00:05:17.480
I'll do whatever you ask.

00:05:17.520 --> 00:05:18.760
Don't abandon me.

00:05:20.680 --> 00:05:21.960
Given your identity,

00:05:22.280 --> 00:05:23.680
you can't stay in the capital.

00:05:34.760 --> 00:05:35.640
Yuanjin!

00:05:40.560 --> 00:05:41.560
All these years,

00:05:43.360 --> 00:05:44.840
did you ever

00:05:46.760 --> 00:05:49.360
truly see me as your sister?

00:06:02.680 --> 00:06:03.560
Xiyu,

00:06:05.120 --> 00:06:06.440
keep an eye on Lady Jifu.

00:06:06.840 --> 00:06:07.840
Understood.

00:07:01.000 --> 00:07:01.960
You think this

00:07:01.960 --> 00:07:04.840
can drive me and Lin Jifu apart?

00:07:09.720 --> 00:07:10.920
Pathetic.

00:07:11.840 --> 00:07:12.800
But,

00:07:13.400 --> 00:07:15.040
someone of your low birth

00:07:15.200 --> 00:07:16.720
will never understand

00:07:18.640 --> 00:07:20.320
that the intricate bonds

00:07:23.040 --> 00:07:25.440
of noble families

00:07:26.040 --> 00:07:27.520
are never based

00:07:27.520 --> 00:07:29.520
on sentiment.

00:07:41.480 --> 00:07:43.200
Thank you for the lesson, Your Highness.

00:07:56.680 --> 00:07:57.520
This face of yours...

00:07:58.960 --> 00:08:00.960
I really want to destroy it now.

00:08:12.520 --> 00:08:14.640
You have deeply offended Jifu.

00:08:15.240 --> 00:08:17.880
She's the type who won't tolerate
even the smallest slight.

00:08:18.400 --> 00:08:19.720
After the ladies' banquet,

00:08:19.720 --> 00:08:20.880
she will surely seek revenge.

00:08:21.720 --> 00:08:23.160
By then, even His Highness

00:08:23.920 --> 00:08:25.560
won't be able to protect you.

00:08:38.320 --> 00:08:39.880
Forbidding me to go

00:08:42.480 --> 00:08:44.560
is exactly what I wanted.

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:47.120
I want you all

00:08:47.160 --> 00:08:49.040
to step unsuspectingly

00:08:49.480 --> 00:08:51.880
into the abyss

00:08:53.480 --> 00:08:56.416
I've prepared for you.

00:09:01.880 --> 00:09:02.960
My body...

00:09:05.760 --> 00:09:06.800
I feel terrible!

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:11.680
My body...

00:09:12.360 --> 00:09:14.800
It feels like ten thousand horses
galloping through me.

00:09:16.560 --> 00:09:18.040
I'll kill Pei Ji.

00:09:18.320 --> 00:09:20.160
I'll kill Xiyan!

00:09:20.160 --> 00:09:21.720
I want...

00:09:25.240 --> 00:09:26.680
I want...

00:09:29.408 --> 00:09:30.720
The Princess Consort said

00:09:30.880 --> 00:09:32.720
you can't take the powder
before the banquet.

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:36.880
No, my lady!

00:09:36.960 --> 00:09:37.952
No!

00:09:38.360 --> 00:09:39.280
Do you know that?

00:09:39.520 --> 00:09:41.200
When human skin meets fire,

00:09:42.440 --> 00:09:44.760
it sounds exactly like
euphoria powder burning.

00:09:45.600 --> 00:09:46.440
No!

00:09:46.440 --> 00:09:48.440
No! My lady, I'll fetch you the powder!

00:09:50.120 --> 00:09:51.136
Can you get some?

00:09:52.040 --> 00:09:53.400
I have a good friend

00:09:54.240 --> 00:09:55.480
serving the Princess Consort.

00:09:55.960 --> 00:09:56.800
I'll beg her

00:09:57.040 --> 00:09:58.360
to steal some for you.

00:09:59.680 --> 00:10:00.640
Good, Xiyu.

00:10:01.040 --> 00:10:02.000
Be quick.

00:10:02.520 --> 00:10:03.720
If you fail,

00:10:05.760 --> 00:10:07.000
tonight

00:10:07.000 --> 00:10:08.560
will be your last night!

00:10:09.320 --> 00:10:10.240
Yes, my lady.

00:10:29.480 --> 00:10:30.880
All this time,

00:10:31.600 --> 00:10:32.680
you've endured so much.

00:10:42.400 --> 00:10:43.840
Without you

00:10:44.080 --> 00:10:45.520
and your mother's secret assistance,

00:10:46.240 --> 00:10:48.000
I would have perished

00:10:48.400 --> 00:10:50.040
like the other maids.

00:10:50.640 --> 00:10:52.400
I willingly became your inside ally.

00:10:53.400 --> 00:10:55.000
When the time comes, I'll arrange

00:10:55.160 --> 00:10:57.040
for Shen Yuanjin to confine me.

00:10:57.800 --> 00:10:59.440
Make her withdrawal symptoms to flare.

00:11:02.880 --> 00:11:04.120
Then give her this.

00:11:05.080 --> 00:11:07.320
It contains Que'nu's
heart-devouring incense.

00:11:09.000 --> 00:11:10.160
You want to trick her

00:11:10.600 --> 00:11:11.800
into suicide?

00:11:12.840 --> 00:11:14.680
That's too lenient for her.

00:11:16.560 --> 00:11:18.720
I'll make her death serve a purpose.

00:11:19.960 --> 00:11:21.280
When she's in nightmares,

00:11:21.600 --> 00:11:23.480
repeat these words to her.

00:11:28.560 --> 00:11:31.120
Walk the path I've laid out for you,

00:11:32.480 --> 00:11:36.400
Lin Jifu.

00:11:44.600 --> 00:11:45.568
My lady,

00:11:45.800 --> 00:11:47.560
you'll attend
the ladies' banquet tomorrow.

00:11:48.400 --> 00:11:49.600
Please take less of that.

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:52.064
Shut up.

00:11:54.400 --> 00:11:56.320
Only this powder comforts me.

00:12:17.360 --> 00:12:18.200
Lin Jifu,

00:12:19.360 --> 00:12:20.320
your retribution

00:12:20.960 --> 00:12:22.160
is approaching.

00:12:32.640 --> 00:12:33.728
Lin Jifu,

00:12:34.280 --> 00:12:35.360
a useless fool

00:12:35.360 --> 00:12:37.000
like you

00:12:37.480 --> 00:12:39.200
is meant to be discarded.

00:12:41.840 --> 00:12:42.752
Mother...

00:12:43.560 --> 00:12:44.512
Mother...

00:12:44.640 --> 00:12:45.840
I was wrong.

00:12:45.960 --> 00:12:47.400
I was wrong.

00:12:48.280 --> 00:12:49.520
Before discarding you,

00:12:50.080 --> 00:12:52.680
they'll drain your last ounce of worth,

00:12:52.880 --> 00:12:54.600
until you're utterly useless.

00:12:56.760 --> 00:12:58.040
Shen Yuanjin,

00:12:58.840 --> 00:13:00.760
I swear I'll make you

00:13:00.760 --> 00:13:02.680
kneel before me

00:13:02.840 --> 00:13:04.640
and beg forgiveness.

00:13:16.080 --> 00:13:17.024
No.

00:13:17.240 --> 00:13:18.336
Mother.

00:13:18.600 --> 00:13:19.520
No.

00:13:20.000 --> 00:13:21.000
Mother.

00:13:21.280 --> 00:13:22.200
Yuanjin.

00:13:22.600 --> 00:13:23.560
Yuanjin.

00:13:24.600 --> 00:13:26.480
Don't abandon me.

00:13:27.360 --> 00:13:28.360
This isn't my fault.

00:13:28.600 --> 00:13:29.640
Go confront her.

00:13:29.640 --> 00:13:31.120
Go confront her.

00:13:48.544 --> 00:13:49.520
My lady,

00:13:49.520 --> 00:13:51.000
the banquet gift list has arrived.

00:13:54.424 --> 00:13:55.424
The Prime Minister's wife

00:13:55.424 --> 00:13:56.720
sends three loads of Luozi dye.

00:13:57.520 --> 00:13:59.800
Her daughter offers
a red coral bracelet.

00:14:00.240 --> 00:14:02.440
Marchioness of Pingyang
sends Mihe incense.

00:14:03.040 --> 00:14:04.200
Luozi dye?

00:14:06.160 --> 00:14:07.360
I remember

00:14:07.800 --> 00:14:10.040
my mother only received two loads.

00:14:10.240 --> 00:14:12.320
The production of Mihe incense
stopped years ago.

00:14:13.040 --> 00:14:14.320
As for red coral,

00:14:14.600 --> 00:14:16.560
that's exclusively worn
by imperial consorts.

00:14:18.080 --> 00:14:19.320
The Minister of War's wife

00:14:19.584 --> 00:14:20.744
sends a tiger-skin cuju ball.

00:14:24.520 --> 00:14:25.560
What's wrong?

00:14:25.800 --> 00:14:27.480
The young master adores cuju.

00:14:27.480 --> 00:14:28.416
I read it wrong.

00:14:28.416 --> 00:14:30.000
T-This is the Princess Consort's list.

00:14:32.160 --> 00:14:33.040
Enough!

00:14:37.720 --> 00:14:39.280
The Prime Minister's wife

00:14:39.280 --> 00:14:40.200
sends

00:14:40.200 --> 00:14:41.640
(Gifts to Lin Jifu of Prince Regent's Mansion)
half a load of Luozi dye.

00:14:42.520 --> 00:14:44.760
Her daughter sends pink coral.

00:14:45.040 --> 00:14:46.440
Marchioness of Pingyang

00:14:46.880 --> 00:14:48.400
sends pearl powder.

00:14:51.840 --> 00:14:54.000
This dowry is meant for me.

00:14:54.880 --> 00:14:57.440
Why are my arrangements
inferior to Shen Yuanjin's?

00:14:58.400 --> 00:14:59.680
By what right?

00:15:05.400 --> 00:15:06.520
With your husband's status.

00:15:06.720 --> 00:15:08.000
They dare not overstep.

00:15:08.080 --> 00:15:09.000
You're lying!

00:15:09.200 --> 00:15:10.120
They clearly...

00:15:10.624 --> 00:15:12.192
(A wife follows her husband's status.)

00:15:12.840 --> 00:15:14.480
(Though swimming in wealth,)

00:15:14.688 --> 00:15:16.440
(merchant families' foundations)

00:15:16.672 --> 00:15:18.360
(remain shallow.)

00:15:18.840 --> 00:15:21.880
(Meant nothing to hereditary nobility.)

00:15:22.280 --> 00:15:23.600
You all look down on me.

00:15:24.720 --> 00:15:26.320
You've all abandoned me.

00:15:34.760 --> 00:15:36.360
Then why should I

00:15:40.440 --> 00:15:42.040
preserve appearances?

